This directory contains test programs that can be compiled and run on Linux
2 programs are built by Makefile:

server:	   A Linux version of HRFReliableDatagramServer, which connects to a
	   HM-TR over RS232 on /dev/ttyUSB0 and listens for requests from a HRFReliableDatagramClient
test_hrf:  A Linux test suite, used during development of the HopeRF library
